    GcdEuclidIteration
    The GcdEuclidIteration class provides an implementation of the Greatest Common Divisor (GCD) computation using the iterative approach of Euclid's algorithm.

    The GcdEuclidRecursion class provides an implementation of the Gcd interface using the recursive Euclidean algorithm to compute the Greatest Common Divisor (GCD) of two integers.
